.sessionlint/

# --- Local-only: internal planning, dev, and test material (not published) ---
# The public repo carries only what someone needs to USE sessionlint.
# These stay on your machine and in the pre-clean-backup tag; never on GitHub.
/MASTER.md
/CLAUDE.md
/scripts/
/fixtures/
*.test.ts

# All internal docs are local-only EXCEPT docs/rules/, which the CLI links to
# (findings print a docs/rules/<id>.md URL — removing it would 404 those links).
/docs/*
!/docs/rules/
